ht-at-their-school-they-found-ancient-roman-ruins-hidden-in-the-basement-180988917/</guid></item><item><title>NASA 实验性 X-59 飞机首次飞行速度超过音速，为“安静”超音速飞机奠定了基础</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-a-first-nasas-experimental-x-59-plane-flew-faster-than-the-speed-of-sound-setting-the-stage-for-quiet-supersonic-aircraft-180988916/</link><description>1973 年，美国禁止超音速飞行飞越其陆地上空，因为超音速飞行会产生震耳欲聋的音爆。专家们正在建造一架飞机，它应该以这样的速度飞行，但只会产生轻微的撞击声</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 20:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-a-first-nasas-experimental-x-59-plane-flew-faster-than-the-speed-of-sound-setting-the-stage-for-quiet-supersonic-aircraft-180988916/</guid></item><item><title>约翰·列侬帮助披头士乐队创作的绘画被重新发现，成为摇滚乐的第一批音乐视频之一</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rediscovered-drawings-john-lennon-helped-create-for-the-beatles-became-one-of-rock-n-rolls-first-music-videos-180988915/</link><description>一位英国收藏家在拍卖会上获得了十幅图画，并将它们借给利物浦披头士博物馆进行临时展览</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 19:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rediscovered-drawings-john-lennon-helped-create-for-the-beatles-became-one-of-rock-n-rolls-first-music-videos-180988915/</guid></item><item><title>哪些模因值得数字化保存？查看英国电影学院为新档案馆选择的在线视频</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/which-memes-deserve-digital-preservation-see-the-online-videos-the-british-film-institute-selected-for-a-new-archive-180988912/</link><description>档案管理员说，几十年来制作的病毒视频、教程、视频博客和直播片段提供了对现代文化和交流的洞察。如果不刻意努力保存，该材料可能会丢失</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 18:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/which-memes-deserve-digital-preservation-see-the-online-videos-the-british-film-institute-selected-for-a-new-archive-180988912/</guid></item><item><title>来认识一下“女巫鳄鱼”吧，这是一种奇怪的古代鳄鱼近亲，有两条腿，没有牙齿，在三叠纪时期在新墨西哥州漫游</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/meet-the-witch-croc-a-strange-ancient-crocodile-relative-with-two-legs-and-no-teeth-that-roamed-new-mexico-during-the-triassic-180988909/</link><description>这种爬行动物是一种长得像恐龙的舒沃龙，它代表了一项期待已久的发现，有助于古生物学家填补化石记录中的空白</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 16:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/meet-the-witch-croc-a-strange-ancient-crocodile-relative-with-two-legs-and-no-teeth-that-roamed-new-mexico-during-the-triassic-180988909/</guid></item><item><title>这种色彩缤纷的鹦鹉在过去的一个世纪里只见过一次。观鸟者刚刚在未开发的印度尼西亚森林中重新发现了它</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-colorful-parakeet-had-been-seen-only-once-over-the-past-century-birders-just-rediscovered-it-in-an-unexplored-indonesian-forest-180988907/</link><description>蓝额澳洲鹦鹉于 20 年代首次通过七个标本被描述，自 2014 年以来就再也没有被发现过。最近徒步旅行的观鸟者拍摄了这种稀有鸟类的照片，并捕捉到了第一批已知的其叫声的录音</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-colorful-parakeet-had-been-seen-only-once-over-the-past-century-birders-just-rediscovered-it-in-an-unexplored-indonesian-forest-180988907/</guid></item><item><title>一艘“几乎难以置信”的沉船令挪威考古学家震惊，船上装满了完好无损的瓷器和奢侈品</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-shipwreck-almost-beyond-belief-stunned-archaeologists-in-norway-with-its-cargo-of-intact-porcelain-dishes-and-luxury-goods-180988910/</link><description>到目前为止，考古学家已从这艘 18 世纪的沉船中发现了 40 件文物，可能还会发现数千件宝藏</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 22:07:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-shipwreck-almost-beyond-belief-stunned-archaeologists-in-norway-with-its-cargo-of-intact-porcelain-dishes-and-luxury-goods-180988910/</guid></item><item><title>银河系中心的超大质量黑洞似乎在吹风——正如科学家长期以来的理论那样</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-supermassive-black-hole-at-the-heart-of-our-galaxy-seems-to-be-blowing-wind-just-as-scientists-long-theorized-180988908/</link><description>自 20 世纪 70 年代以来，科学家们一直在寻找这种微风的证据。他们已经看到来自其他黑洞的强烈风，但他们一直在努力观察银河系中心的黑洞</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 19:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-supermassive-black-hole-at-the-heart-of-our-galaxy-seems-to-be-blowing-wind-just-as-scientists-long-theorized-180988908/</guid></item><item><title>这座大教堂矗立在巴塞罗那之上已有 144 年历史。中央塔现已竣工，教皇利奥十四世准备访问</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/sagrada-familia-basilica-has-been-rising-above-barcelona-for-144-years-with-its-central-tower-now-complete-pope-leo-XIV-prepares-to-visit-180988906/</link><description>当安东尼·高迪（Antoni Gaudí）对圣家堂（Sagrada Família）提出雄心勃勃的愿景时，他知道自己无法活着看到它的竣工。建筑师去世一百年后，最高的塔已达到顶峰</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 19:14:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/sagrada-familia-basilica-has-been-rising-above-barcelona-for-144-years-with-its-central-tower-now-complete-pope-leo-XIV-prepares-to-visit-180988906/</guid></item><item><title>在二战领袖温斯顿·丘吉尔去世后首次举办的英国大型回顾展上，令人惊讶地一睹他的消遣——绘画</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/catch-a-surprising-glimpse-at-wwii-leader-winston-churchills-pastime-painting-at-the-first-major-british-retrospective-since-his-death-180988905/</link><description>伦敦展出的 50 多幅油画详细描述了首相远离战争、演讲和政治的安静时刻</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 17:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/catch-a-surprising-glimpse-at-wwii-leader-winston-churchills-pastime-painting-at-the-first-major-british-retrospective-since-his-death-180988905/</guid></item><item><title>科学家研究火蝾螈已有 250 多年的历史。他们刚刚发现这些生物在紫外线下会发光</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-have-been-studying-these-salamanders-for-more-than-250-years-they-just-discovered-the-creatures-glow-under-uv-light-180988900/</link><description>火蝾螈是欧洲研究最深入的两栖动物之一，具有生物荧光，这意味着它们可以吸收外部光源的一种波长的光，然后以另一种波长重新发射光</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 15:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-have-been-studying-these-salamanders-for-more-than-250-years-they-just-discovered-the-creatures-glow-under-uv-light-180988900/</guid></item><item><title>是什么决定了蜜蜂的版税？一项研究表明，皇后区不仅需要独特的饮食，还需要专门建造的王室</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-determines-royalty-among-honeybees-not-just-a-distinct-diet-queens-also-need-specially-built-regal-chambers-a-study-suggests-180988899/</link><description>未来蚁后成长的花生形隔间似乎在发育中发挥着重要作用。蜡与蜂巢其他部分的蜡具有化学和物理差异</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-determines-royalty-among-honeybees-not-just-a-distinct-diet-queens-also-need-specially-built-regal-chambers-a-study-suggests-180988899/</guid></item><item><title>巴哈马附近发现的沉船引起了研究人员的兴趣，因为它们可能与真正的加勒比海盗有关</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shipwrecks-discovered-near-the-bahamas-tantalize-researchers-with-possible-ties-to-the-real-pirates-of-the-caribbean-180988901/</link><description>由考古学家和电影制片人组成的团队获准在拿骚港的禁区潜水，发现了六艘沉船，其中三艘疑似与海盗时代有关</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 13:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shipwrecks-discovered-near-the-bahamas-tantalize-researchers-with-possible-ties-to-the-real-pirates-of-the-caribbean-180988901/</guid></item><item><title>参观纽约一家医院为病童绘制的获救和修复的《爱丽丝梦游仙境》壁画</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-rescued-and-restored-alice-in-wonderland-mural-painted-for-sick-children-at-a-new-york-hospital-180988898/</link><description>艾布拉姆·尚帕尼尔 (Abram Champanier) 的《爱丽丝梦游仙境》是受联邦艺术项目委托创作的，该项目是一项在公共场所倡导美国艺术的新政计划</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 20:24:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-rescued-and-restored-alice-in-wonderland-mural-painted-for-sick-children-at-a-new-york-hospital-180988898/</guid></item><item><title>科学家用冰人奥茨木乃伊尸体上发现的酵母制作酸面包</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-made-sourdough-bread-with-yeast-found-on-otzi-the-icemans-mummified-body-180988894/</link><description>1991 年在阿尔卑斯山发现的遗迹是多种细菌、真菌和酵母的家园</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 19:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-made-sourdough-bread-with-yeast-found-on-otzi-the-icemans-mummified-body-180988894/</guid></item><item><title>NASA 在与火星轨道飞行器失去联系数月后正式结束 MAVEN 任务</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/nasa-officially-ends-the-maven-mission-months-after-losing-contact-with-the-mars-orbiter-180988897/</link><description>该机构最后一次收到该航天器的消息是在 12 月 6 日。恢复的碎片数据表明，MAVEN 正在意外旋转，暗示其轨道发生了变化并耗尽了电池电量</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 18:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/nasa-officially-ends-the-maven-mission-months-after-losing-contact-with-the-mars-orbiter-180988897/</guid></item><item><title>乔治·华盛顿在领导民兵时记录了啤酒的配方。感谢纽约公共图书馆，今年夏天您可以吸收这段历史</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/george-washington-recorded-a-recipe-for-beer-while-leading-a-militia-thanks-to-the-new-york-public-library-you-can-imbibe-that-history-this-summer-180988896/</link><description>为了庆祝美国成立 250 周年，图书馆与一家啤酒厂合作生产了开国元勋的啤酒，并推出了更符合现代口味的更新版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 17:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/george-washington-recorded-a-recipe-for-beer-while-leading-a-militia-thanks-to-the-new-york-public-library-you-can-imbibe-that-history-this-summer-180988896/</guid></item><item><title>汤加的大规模火山喷发清除了2022年本国的部分甲烷排放，暗示了应对气候变化的方法</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/tongas-enormous-volcanic-eruption-cleaned-up-part-of-its-own-methane-emissions-in-2022-hinting-at-a-way-to-fight-climate-change-180988893/</link><description>研究人员分析了火山羽流的卫星图像，发现了强效温室气体已经分解的证据。科学家表示，这项工作可以为旨在缓解全球变暖的人工干预措施提供信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 16:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ton